Source  : ideas_database.db — idea score 90.3/100

Domain      : HealthTech
Technology  : Fine-tuned LLM + FHIR R4 + Medical NLP
Problem     : Clinicians spend 50% of their time on paperwork, not patients.
Solution    : NLP pipeline converting free-text notes to structured FHIR R4 JSON.
Impact      : ~60% admin time reduction per note

Novelty: 96/100 | Feasibility: 77/100 | Impact: 96/100

FHIR resources generated: Condition, MedicationRequest, Observation, Procedure, Patient
Standards: ICD-10, SNOMED-CT, LOINC, RxNorm, HL7 FHIR R4
